casebody.data:
No. 10M84. Jacqueline Shiplet, Petitioner v. Thomas J. Vilsack, Secretary of Agriculture. 563 U.S. 901, 131 S. Ct. 1806,

179 L. Ed. 2d 651,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 2498. March 28, 2011.

Motion for leave to file a petition for writ of certiorari with the *652supplemental appendix under seal denied without prejudice to filing a renewed motion together with either a redacted supplemental appendix, or an explanation as to why the supplemental appendix may not be redacted, within 30 days.
